              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uibutton/1624018-settitle"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and can serve as a replacement for those methods. Alternatively, you can use a configuration in combination with these other methods and adopt new button behaviors and appearance without rewriting your customized "
            },
